### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@contentType = application/json

### The basic request
GET {{baseUrl}}

### Get all tasks
GET {{baseUrl}}/tasks

### Get one task
GET {{baseUrl}}/tasks/{{taskId}}

### Create new task
# @name createTask
POST {{baseUrl}}/tasks
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "title": "Kairos API",
  "description": "Another serverside Nest JS application.",
  "status": "DONE"
}

### Set the task id
@taskId = {{ createTask.response.body.id }}

### Validation error - status is incorrect
POST {{baseUrl}}/tasks
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "title": "",
  "description": "",
  "status": ""
}

### Update the task status
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/tasks/{{taskId}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "status": "IN_PROGRESS"
}

### Delete the task
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/tasks/{{taskId}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}